### get all items

# @name getItems
GET {{baseUrl}}/items

### set item id 上のレスポンスで返ってきた値をそのまま使える

@itemId = {{ getItems.response.body.$.[0].id }}

### create new item

POST {{baseUrl}}/items
Authorization: Bearer <token here>
Content-Type: {{Content-Type}}

{
  "description": "Complete this course",
  "name": "what about let's encrypt",
  "price": 1000
}

### get item by id

# GET {{baseUrl}}/items/c0b1e45a-de4e-496a-b2b2-bf360a5dfa30
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}

### update item status

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer <ここにsignin で取得したトークン>
Content-Type: {{Content-Type}}

{
  "name": "what about let's encrypt",
  "status": "ON_SALE"
}

### delete item

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer <ここにsignin で取得したトークン>

